                    <item name="Size" type_name="gh_single" type_code="5">15</item>
                    <item name="Text" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">This installer will add the required HB-REVIVE libraries to the Ladybug Tools’ Python interpreter which is installed on your computer. 
Specifically, it will:
- Download and add a new ‘Honeybee-REVIVE’ plugin to your Ladybug Tools installation.
- Download and add a new ‘PH-ADORB’ plugin to your Ladybug Tools installation.
- Download and add new HB-REVIVE Grasshopper Components to your Grasshopper ‘User Objects’ folder which will then be available for use in your Grasshopper environment

NOTE: The Honeybee-REVIVE Plugin is currently compatible with Ladybug Tools version v1.8.47 or newer only.</item>
