                    <item name="Text" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">We are sorry about that, but for Windows users it is REQUIRED for you to be running Rhino in ‘Admin’ mode in order to properly
install the Honeybee-REVIVE packages into your Ladybug-Tools python environment. If you are NOT in 
‘admin’ mode, the install will fail. This is caused by the built-in behavior of python, and not something that can be changed.</item>
